</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="87.[151,1437,150,1905]" box="[199,1417,1770,1797]" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,389,1770,1797]" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">Natural history.</emphasis>
